{"type":"text","timestamp":1775863984774,"sessionID":"ses_28644a1e1ffeXevK8ggqv8mK5C","part":{"id":"prt_d79bdb7f9001TbpI4SjSNXLXaB","messageID":"msg_d79bd7983001iQCONT1qQwuZKc","sessionID":"ses_28644a1e1ffeXevK8ggqv8mK5C","type":"text","text":"Based on my analysis of the AR-011 change records and implementation files, here is the summary:\n\n---\n\n## AR-011 Archive Summary: Router JWT 认证与签发\n\n### What Was Completed\n\n**Core Implementation (100% complete):**\n\n1. **JWT Types & Structures** (`jwt_types.go`)\n   - TokenClaims, TokenPair, TokenMetadata types\n   - TokenManager interface\n   - Request/Response DTOs for token operations\n   - Context key management for claims\n\n2. **JWT Error Handling** (`jwt_errors.go`)\n   - JWTError struct with Code/Message/Cause\n   - 9 sentinel errors (ErrTokenExpired, ErrTokenInvalid, etc.)\n   - Helper functions (IsJWTError, GetJWTErrorCode, etc.)\n\n3. **JWT Configuration** (`jwt_config.go`)\n   - JWTConfig with environment variable support\n   - Validation rules (RSA key size >= 2048, expiry checks)\n   - Builder pattern methods\n\n4. **Core JWT Manager** (`jwt.go`)\n   - RSA-2048 key generation\n   - RS256 token signing & validation\n   - Token pair generation (access + refresh tokens)\n   - Token refresh mechanism with jti claim\n   - Kubernetes Secret integration for key persistence\n   - Key rotation with versioning support\n   - Multi-key validation during rotation\n\n5. **JWT Middleware** (`jwt_middleware.go`)\n   - Authenticate middleware (Bearer token extraction)\n   - OptionalAuthenticate middleware\n   - RequireSession middleware\n   - RequireClaims middleware\n\n6. **HTTP Handlers** (`jwt_handlers.go`)\n   - POST /v1/tokens (token generation)\n   - POST /v1/tokens/refresh\n   - GET /v1/keys/public\n   - POST /v1/tokens/validate\n\n---\n\n### What Was Deferred\n\n**Testing Tasks (Tasks 12-18):**\n- Comprehensive unit test coverage (target: >= 80%)\n- Integration tests for token lifecycle\n- JWT-Session flow integration tests\n- JWT error scenario tests\n- Metrics exposure verification\n- AR-009/AR-010 compatibility verification\n\n**Session Manager Integration (Task 8):**\n- Session-aware token generation methods\n- Session validation in JWT middleware\n- Full integration with SessionManager\n\n**Enhanced Metrics (Task 9):**\n- Prometheus metrics (counters, histograms, gauges)\n   - `agentcube_jwt_tokens_generated_total`\n   - `agentcube_jwt_tokens_validated_total`\n   - `agentcube_jwt_validation_duration_seconds`\n\n**Documentation (Task 21):**\n- Package-level documentation with examples\n- Configuration guide\n- Key rotation documentation\n\n**Final Verification Tasks (22-24):**\n- Race condition testing\n- golint/godoc verification\n- Full test suite validation\n\n---\n\n### Files Delivered\n\n| File | Status | Lines |\n|------|--------|-------|\n| `pkg/router/jwt.go` | Complete | 638 |\n| `pkg/router/jwt_types.go` | Complete | 266 |\n| `pkg/router/jwt_errors.go` | Complete | 154 |\n| `pkg/router/jwt_config.go` | Complete | 143 |\n| `pkg/router/jwt_middleware.go` | Complete | 237 |\n| `pkg/router/jwt_handlers.go` | Complete | 271 |\n\n**Stage:** ST-3 completed (Core implementation)  \n**Pending:** ST-4 (Testing & Integration)","time":{"start":1775863984772,"end":1775863984772}}}
